title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Apr 6 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Apr 6 2022
description:
We're on the way to the 5th and 6th shots. China's zero-covid policy. Jimmy Fallon makes fun of the CDC. Ken Cuccinelli, former Virginia AG, talks to Clay and Buck about the new movie: “Rigged: The Zuckerberg Funded Plot to Defeat Donald Trump.” Joe Biden caught in lie about Hunter's business partner, wrote recommendation letter for person he claims not to know. Climate nuts want you to set your thermostat to 82 degrees. C&B end the show with a call.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
